paexec:
 - rename paexec_reorder to pareorder
 - -y -mt='magic string'
 - -n 'server1 server2 +5' two remote servers and five local
 - paexec -C [OPTIONS] cmd arg1 arg2..
 - -X -- suppress calculator's output
 - paexec_reorder -x
 - mt= together with -x is useless => error message
 - refresh presentation for lvee-2011 and make it a part of documentation
 - trim spaces in -t argument and then check it for emptyness
 - Option -I like in xargs (in combination with -x)
 - Option -n%'node_[1-20,22-30]'
 - non-blocking write(2) for sending task to the slave hosts/CPUs.
 - SIGINFO for displaying current status of tasks
 - SIGUSR1 for trying restore connection to dead client hosts
